text: (Tya veli misracya ajijaci patni) mhanali, haca to, jyacyavisayi tumhi mala bare-va'ita bolata hotya. Mi sarva prakare yacyakaduna apali iccha purna karu icchile, parantu ha niskalanka rahila ani je kahi mi yala sangata ahe, jara te ha karanara nahi tara niscitaca yala kaidi banavile ja'ila ani khatrine ha motha apamanita ho'ila
